---
import OptimizedImage from "@/components/utilities/OptimizedImage.astro";
---

<section
  id="featuresSectionEn"
  class="py-14 text-[#262626] md:py-20 dark:text-white">
  <h1
    class="mx-auto mb-2 text-center font-bold sm:text-6xl md:text-6xl lg:mb-5 lg:text-7xl">
    The right choice changes everything.
  </h1>
  <h2
    class="mx-auto mb-4 text-center sm:text-6xl md:text-2xl lg:mb-20 lg:text-3xl">
    We work to standards that leave no room for compromise.
  </h2>
  <div class="mx-auto w-full max-w-425 px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-10">
    <div
      id="featuresCarouselEn"
      class="no-scrollbar flex snap-x snap-mandatory gap-5 overflow-x-auto scroll-smooth pb-2 md:grid md:grid-cols-2 md:overflow-visible lg:grid-cols-4">
      <article
        class="feature-card block w-full min-w-full snap-center rounded-2xl border border-[#d1d5db] bg-white p-6 text-[#262626] shadow-xs md:min-w-0 dark:border-white/20 dark:bg-[#202224] dark:text-white">
        <OptimizedImage
          src="/images/logo.svg"
          alt="Experience you can rely on"
          class="aspect-4/3 w-full rounded-xl !bg-white object-contain p-6"
          loading="lazy"
        />
        <h5
          class="feature-card-title mt-6 mb-2 text-2xl font-semibold tracking-tight">
          Experience you can trust
        </h5>
        <p class="feature-card-body mb-6">
          Years of production, installation, and completed projects have taught us
          one thing: quality is never accidental.
          <br />
          Every window and door is built on proven expertise and tightly controlled
          processes from start to finish. That is how we deliver security, reliability,
          and performance that lasts.
        </p>
      </article>

      <article
        class="feature-card block w-full min-w-full snap-center rounded-2xl border border-[#d1d5db] bg-white p-6 text-[#262626] shadow-xs md:min-w-0 dark:border-white/20 dark:bg-[#202224] dark:text-white">
        <OptimizedImage
          src="/images/dettaglio.avif"
          alt="Craft in every detail"
          class="aspect-4/3 w-full rounded-xl object-cover"
          loading="lazy"
        />
        <h5
          class="feature-card-title mt-6 mb-2 text-2xl font-semibold tracking-tight">
          Details define the result
        </h5>
        <p class="feature-card-body mb-6">
          We go far beyond technical performance.<br />
          We focus on finishes, alignment, assembly, and millimetric precision.<br />
          Because true quality lives in the details you may not notice at first,
          but appreciate for years.
        </p>
      </article>

      <article
        class="feature-card block w-full min-w-full snap-center rounded-2xl border border-[#d1d5db] bg-white p-6 text-[#262626] shadow-xs md:min-w-0 dark:border-white/20 dark:bg-[#202224] dark:text-white">
        <OptimizedImage
          src="/images/madeinitaly.svg"
          alt="Proudly Made in Italy"
          class="aspect-4/3 w-full rounded-xl !bg-white object-contain p-6"
          loading="lazy"
        />
        <h5
          class="feature-card-title mt-6 mb-2 text-2xl font-semibold tracking-tight">
          Proud to be Made in Italy
        </h5>
        <p class="feature-card-body mb-6">
          We craft every frame in house, combining advanced technology with
          artisan-level care.<br />
          From design to final build, every phase is under our direct control.
          A Paolucci window is not just a product. It is the expression of an
          Italian quality chain you can feel every day.
        </p>
      </article>

      <article
        class="feature-card block w-full min-w-full snap-center rounded-2xl border border-[#d1d5db] bg-white p-6 text-[#262626] shadow-xs md:min-w-0 dark:border-white/20 dark:bg-[#202224] dark:text-white">
        <OptimizedImage
          src="public/images/customer_care.avif"
          alt="Support that stays with you"
          class="aspect-4/3 w-full rounded-xl object-cover"
          loading="lazy"
        />
        <h5
          class="feature-card-title mt-6 mb-2 text-2xl font-semibold tracking-tight">
          Support that stays with you
        </h5>
        <p class="feature-card-body mb-6">
          Our work does not end when installation is complete.<br />
          We provide after-sales care, technical support, and real availability
          whenever you need us.<br />
          Choosing Paolucci means having a trusted partner over time.
        </p>
      </article>
    </div>

    <div class="mt-6 flex items-center justify-center gap-3 md:hidden">
      <button
        type="button"
        data-carousel-prev="featuresCarouselEn"
        aria-label="Previous card"
        class="inline-flex h-10 w-10 items-center justify-center rounded-full border border-[#d0d0d0] bg-white shadow-xs transition hover:bg-[#f2f2f2]">
        <svg
          xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg"
          class="h-5 w-5"
          viewBox="0 0 24 24"
          fill="none">
          <path
            d="m15 6-6 6 6 6"
            stroke="currentColor"
            stroke-width="2"
            stroke-linecap="round"
            stroke-linejoin="round">
          </path>
        </svg>
      </button>
      <button
        type="button"
        data-carousel-next="featuresCarouselEn"
        aria-label="Next card"
        class="inline-flex h-10 w-10 items-center justify-center rounded-full border border-[#d0d0d0] bg-white shadow-xs transition hover:bg-[#f2f2f2]">
        <svg
          xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg"
          class="h-5 w-5"
          viewBox="0 0 24 24"
          fill="none">
          <path
            d="m9 6 6 6-6 6"
            stroke="currentColor"
            stroke-width="2"
            stroke-linecap="round"
            stroke-linejoin="round">
          </path>
        </svg>
      </button>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<script is:inline>
  (() => {
    const carousel = document.getElementById("featuresCarouselEn");
    if (!carousel) return;

    const prev = document.querySelector(
      '[data-carousel-prev="featuresCarouselEn"]',
    );
    const next = document.querySelector(
      '[data-carousel-next="featuresCarouselEn"]',
    );

    const step = () => carousel.clientWidth + 20;

    prev?.addEventListener("click", () => {
      carousel.scrollBy({ left: -step(), behavior: "smooth" });
    });

    next?.addEventListener("click", () => {
      carousel.scrollBy({ left: step(), behavior: "smooth" });
    });
  })();
</script>

<style is:global>
  .no-scrollbar {
    -ms-overflow-style: none;
    scrollbar-width: none;
  }
  .no-scrollbar::-webkit-scrollbar {
    display: none;
  }
</style>
